Invocation Name: french counter
des:
You can use French Counter to have Alexa count for you in French!

After you launch the skill, Alexa will ask you to provide a number. Alexa will count up to the number in French.

You should provide your number in English. The maximum number accepted is 1,000.

To begin, say, "Alexa, launch French Counter!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
